-- Gold Futures Drop as Much as 0.7% After Fluctuating Between Gains, Losses
-- Patrick McKiernan
-- 2010-07-08T13:48:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/gold-futures-drop-as-much-as-0-7-after-fluctuating-between-gains-losses.html

          
          
             Gold futures for August delivery fell
$6.20, or 0.5 percent, to $1,192.70 an ounce at 9:47 a.m. on the
Comex in New York. Earlier, the price fluctuated between gains
and losses after climbing as much as 0.8 percent.  
          
          


  


        